Lab 4: Snowfall with Projections

Christopher Jordan
CSCI4229 Fall 2014

Utilizing code provided from William Schreuder via the ex9 program

Approximate time: 10 hours

Key bindings
  m          Toggle between perspective and orthogonal
  f          Toggle between snow frozen in time and falling snow
  n          For new snow view in frozen in time mode
  +/-        Changes field of view for perspective
  a          Toggle axes
  arrows     Change view angle
  PgDn/PgUp  Zoom in and out
  0          Reset view angle
  ESC        Exit
